Title: Fix dynamic configuration executing only phase 1 in some distributed setups
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: dcd
Date: 1612349476
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

Since werk #11972 (2.0.0b5) some dynamic configuration connections in
distributed setups were only executing phase 1 of the dynamic configuration.
As a result the connections were not creating new hosts anymore.
